OL,5,G0325 The Chase
OL,6,     FBradley Walsh presents as Gary
OL,7,     Ffrom London, Ginny from Falmouth,
OL,8,     FBeth from Manchester and Wesley
OL,9,     Ffrom Bristol pit their wits
OL,10,     Fagainst one of the ruthless
OL,11,     FChasers in the hope of winning a
OL,12,     Fpotential prize pot worth
OL,13,     Fthousands of pounds. They work as
OL,14,     Fa team and play strategically to
OL,15,     Fanswer general knowledge questions
OL,16,     Fagainst the clock and race down
OL,17,     Fthe game board to the exit without
OL,18,     Fbeing caught
